{"tid":1549110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家嘈夠未？聽日有咩活動？","createTime":"2019-09-07T08:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T11:50:26.000Z","uid":69202,"like":185,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"f48f4449faa938671e590311419655bd688bb786","tid":1549110,"uid":69202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:15:05.000Z","msg":"個個係度嘈fc問題 係呀真係有手足被強姦 甚至犧牲咗 咁又點？<br />\n我地都要贏依場仗 先可以全力清算到黑警同政府 輸咗嘅話真相永遠石沉大海 只會清算返我地手足<br />\n個個係度嘈 帶風向 有咩用 不如好好宣傳聽日 叫更多人出嚟好過啦<br />\n我地係要贏呀 依家文宣人數 勇武人數都需要增加 大家唔好再抝好冇<br />\n雨革就係咁樣而輸 你地醒目少少啦 成日比人帶風向<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8c32a4cee1e3ae22f7e993986cae6dbd8dc74a","tid":1549110,"uid":69202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:15:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4014b208cd4f3f098ca51298681ffd97ef6b9d1","tid":1549110,"uid":69202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41d220212d6d714426453d4e5ba7ab21cb288e79","tid":1549110,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6dd641385a4abf229607ab9b52ea1395bf71adc","tid":1549110,"uid":292151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"唔該幫幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n908 美領！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549074</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"07c53208ae19f9c4f1ef0bbe62812f01e32f6457","tid":1549110,"uid":273466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"9月8日香港人權與民主祈禱會<br />\n<br />\n明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\nPrayer Meeting for Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy<br />\n<br />\nThe Letter of No Objection for the meeting (at Chater Garden) and the procession (to US Consulate) has been issued.<br />\n<br />\nThe Meeting<br />\nVenue: Chater Garden, Central<br />\nTime: 13:30-18:30<br />\nSubtheme for each session:<br />\n&quot;Chosen People&quot;, &quot;Praise in Prison&quot;, &quot;Judgement Shall Come&quot;,  &quot;God Bless America&quot;<br />\n<br />\n※※ Signatures for the Declaration of the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy will be collected at Chater Garden until 14:30, then be submitted to US Consulate in the procession ※※<br />\n<br />\nThe Procession<br />\nAssemble Point: Chater Garden near Queensway<br />\nAssemble Time: 14:30<br />\nRoute: Start at Chater Garden, go along Garden Road and submit petition letter to US Consulate General at public activity area near bus stop at Lower Albert Road<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dEdZcy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dEdZcy.jpg&h=9d27a5d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjKYqSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjKYqSz.jpg&h=ba976118&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffeb594177524b1cd5c553c5c8d95a1b109f648f","tid":1549110,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"係囉，做下實事仲好啦，成日開post 引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abac0d0dbc469b4196f96bf8c974670c13c7e52c","tid":1549110,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"[人在機場 個人意見] 塞香港站+阻人入青馬就夠<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1548911\" data-